      <title xtrc="GSAR" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">503.1004</ph> Contract
clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d68e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li id="GLpZZC" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d67e18" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  <ph id="dz3xsi8n" class="- topic/ph ">In accordance
with FAR <xref href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/part-3#FAR_3_1004"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref ">3.1004</xref>(b)(1)(i), GSA
has established a lower threshold for the inclusion of FAR clause
at <xref href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/part-52#FAR_52_203_14"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref ">52.203-14</xref>. Insert
the clause in solicitations and contracts funded with disaster assistance
funds expected to be at or above $1,000,000.</ph>
               </p>
            </li>
            <li id="Gjxcsf" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/li ">
