                  <ph id="v2yj02ia" class="- topic/ph ">The information required
by FAR <xref href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/part-3#FAR_3_1004"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref ">3.1004</xref>(b)(2) is as
follows:</ph>
               </p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li id="mkLKBO" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/li ">
